msgid "`LIBFOO_INSTALL_OPTS`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/_pkg-install-opts-with-install.md:3
msgid "Support added for path-like values."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/_pkg-install-opts-with-install.md:6
msgid ""
"Provides a means to pass command line options into the installation process."
" This option can be defined as a dictionary of string pairs or a list with "
"strings -- either way defined will generate argument values to include in "
"the installation event. This field is optional."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/_pkg-install-opts-with-install.md:29
msgid ""
"Defining custom install options will prevent the default `install` target "
"from being added. Users looking to utilize the `install` target for the "
"install stage with custom arguments should explicitly include the `install` "
"target in their options."
msgstr ""
